"Cut food into small pieces for young children|Chew food thoroughly before swallowing|Avoid talking or laughing while eating|Keep small objects away from toddlers|Learn the Heimlich maneuver|Supervise young children during meals",
"给幼儿切小块食物|食物充分咀嚼后再吞咽|吃饭时避免说话或大笑|让小物品远离幼儿|学习海姆立克手法|用餐时监督幼儿",
"Encourage forceful coughing if partial blockage|Heimlich maneuver for conscious adults|Back blows and chest thrusts for infants|Abdominal thrusts for children over 1|Begin CPR if person becomes unconscious|Call emergency services immediately",
