"Wear proper protective gear during sports|Ensure adequate calcium and vitamin D intake|Remove tripping hazards from home|Use proper technique when lifting heavy objects|Wear appropriate footwear for activities|Build bone strength through weight-bearing exercise",
"运动时穿适当防护装备|确保充足钙和维生素D摄入|移除家中绊倒隐患|搬重物时使用正确技术|活动时穿适当鞋类|通过负重运动增强骨骼",
"Immobilize the injured area without realigning|Apply ice wrapped in cloth to reduce swelling|Call emergency services for suspected fractures|X-ray or CT scan for diagnosis|Casting or splinting for stable fractures|Surgical fixation for complex fractures",
"固定受伤区域不要复位|用布包裹冰敷减轻肿胀|疑似骨折拨打急救电话|X光或CT扫描诊断|稳定骨折的石膏或夹板|复杂骨折的手术固定",
